{
  "title": "🔍 Healthcare NOC — Device Detail Drill-Down",
  "description": "Device-level detailed monitoring dashboard. Drill down from NOC Overview to inspect specific device metrics including health, network, medical device specifics, environmental data, and alert history.",
  "layout_type": "ordered",
  "tags": [
    "vertical:healthcare",
    "dd-demo-toolkit:true",
    "dashboard-type:noc-detail"
  ],
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "device_id",
      "prefix": "device_id",
      "available_values": []
    },
    {
      "name": "device_type",
      "prefix": "device_type",
      "available_values": []
    },
    {
      "name": "floor",
      "prefix": "floor",
      "available_values": []
    },
    {
      "name": "wing",
      "prefix": "wing",
      "available_values": []
    },
    {
      "name": "department",
      "prefix": "department",
      "available_values": []
    },
    {
      "name": "manufacturer",
      "prefix": "manufacturer",
      "available_values": []
    }
  ],
  "widgets": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "# 🔍 Device Detail Drill-Down\n\n**Select a device using the template variables above** (`device_id`, `device_type`, `floor`, `wing`, `department`, `manufacturer`), or **click through from the NOC Overview dashboard**.\n\nThis dashboard shows real-time health, network performance, medical device specifics, environmental context, and alert history for the selected device(s).",
        "background_color": "vivid_blue",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "center",
        "show_tick": false,
        "has_padding": true
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "title": "📋 Device Identity Header",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 3,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Online Status",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1"
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:hospital.device.online{$device_id,$device_type,$floor,$wing,$department,$manufacturer}"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "scalar"
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 0,
              "conditional_formats": [
                {
                  "comparator": "==",
                  "value": 1,
                  "color": "vivid_green"
                },
                {
                  "comparator": "!=",
                  "value": 1,
                  "color": "vivid_red"
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 3
            }
          },
